OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe south fading as overcast
OL,7,Fconditions extend southwards, with
OL,8,Fareas of low cloud and the odd spot of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. Light winds but breezy along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter and
OL,13,Fa little cooler from the north. Mostly
OL,14,Fdry, although a few mostly light
OL,15,Fshowers are still possible. Winds
OL,16,Fremaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
